init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm in the back of an alien's spaceship," said Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Can you see the alien?" asked Ari.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: One of them is green, one of them is red, and one of them is blue."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Probably when the alien ship is parked right outside the International Space Station," replied Matt.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm in the backseat of my car," said Matt.
